tered the document number correctly and that it\'s valid. ","show":"I am purchasing as a business","hide":"I\'m not purchasing as a business","summary":{"tax_label":"GST","info_message":"Goods and Services Tax (GST)"},"region":{"QC":{"tax_info_label":"Are you purchasing as a business and have a GST / QST number?","tax_info_label_field":"Your QST number","placeholder_label":"QST number","valid_message":"Your QST number has been successfully confirmed!","invalid_message":"It wasn\'t possible to confirm your QST number","cannot_apply_discount":"Something went wrong. The corporate document you entered does not have a QST registration, so it\'s not possible to make the purchase tax free. To complete your purchase, please check your registration status and try again or remove the corporate document number.","info_message":"If you are purchasing as a business from Quebec and you have a QST number, your purchase is tax free. Verify that you have entered the document number correctly and that it\'s valid. ","show":"Add GST / QST Number","hide":"Remove GST / QST Number","summary":{"tax_label":"QST","info_message":"Quebec Sales Tax (QST)"}},"ON":{"tax_info_label":"Are you purchasing as a business and have a GST/HST number?","tax_info_label_field":"Your GST/HST number","placeholder_label":"GST/HST number","valid_message":"Your GST number has been verified!","invalid_message":"It was not possible to verify your GST number","cannot_apply_discount":"Something went wrong. The corporate document you entered does not have a GST/HST registration, so it\'s not possible to make the purchase tax free. To complete your purchase, please check your registration status and try again or remove the corporate document number.","info_message":"If you are purchasing as a business from Canada and you have a GST/HST number, your purchase is tax free. Verify that you have entered the document number correctly and that it\'s valid. ","show":"Add GST/HST Number","hide":"Remove GST/HST Number","summary":{"tax_label":"HST","info_message":"Harmonized Sales Tax (HST)"},"SK":{"tax_info_label":"Are you purchasing as a business and have a GST/PST number?","tax_info_label_field":"Your GST/PST number","placeholder_label":"GST/PST number","valid_message":"Your GST/PST number was successfully verified!","invalid_message":"It was not possible to verify your GST/PST number","cannot_apply_discount":"Something went wrong. The corporate document you entered does not have a GST/PST registration, so it\'s not possible to make the purchase tax free. To complete your purchase, please check your registration status and try again, or remove the corporate document number.","info_message":"If you\'re purchasing as a business in Canada and you have a GST/PST number, your purchase is tax free. Verify that you have entered the document number correctly and that it\'s valid. ","show":"Add GST/PST Number","hide":"Remove GST/PST Number","summary":{"tax_label":"PST","info_message":"Provincial Sales Tax (PST)"}}}}},"chile":{"tax_info_label":"Are you purchasing as a company and have a RUT?","tax_info_label_field":"Add RUT","placeholder_label":"RUT","valid_message":"Your RUT has been successfully confirmed!","invalid_message":"It wasn\'t possible to confirm your RUT","cannot_apply_discount":"Ooops! This RUT is not valid. Make sure you\'ve entered the same numbers as registered. ","info_message":"If you are purchasing as a business and have a valid RUT, your purchase is tax-free. Check if you have entered the number correctly and if your RUT registration is active. ","show":"I am purchasing as a business","hide":"I\'m not purchasing as a business","summary":{"tax_label":"IVA"}},"general":{"tax_info_label":"Are you making the purchase as a company or self-employed individual and you have a VAT number?","tax_info_label_field":"Add Intra-Community VAT","placeholder_label":"VAT number","valid_message":"Intra-Community VAT entered is valid","invalid_message":"The Intra-Community VAT is invalid. Please check if you\'ve entered the correct numbers and letters from your registration. ","cannot_apply_discount":"Something went wrong. The company document you provided is valid, but it is not possible to make the purchase tax-free due to a restriction. To complete your purchase, please check your registration status and try again or remove your company document.","info_message":"If purchasing as a company or self-employed with Intra-Community VAT, your purchase is free of VAT. Make sure you have typed the correct numbers and letters from your registration.","show":"Add Intra-Community VAT","hide":"Delete Intra-Community VAT","summary":{"tax_label":"VAT","info_message":"Intra-Community VAT"}},"mexico":{"tax_info_label":"Do you have an RFC (Registro Federal de Contribuyentes)?","tax_info_label_field":"Enter RFC number","placeholder_label":"RFC number","valid_message":"The RFC entered is valid","invalid_message":"RFC is not valid. Make sure you\'ve entered the same numbers and letters from your registration. ","cannot_apply_discount":"Ooops! This RFC is not valid. Make sure you\'ve entered the same numbers as registered. ","info_message":"As determined by federal law, starting June 1st, 2020, all buyers in Mexico will be subject to an IVA tax.","show":"Show RFC","hide":"Hide RFC","summary":{"tax_label":"IVA","info_message":"As determined by federal law, starting June 1st, 2020, all buyers in Mexico will be subject to an IVA tax."}},"argentina":{"tip_message":"You can choose and use your  CUIT / CUIL or DNI"},"unitedstates":{"summary":{"tax_label":"Sales tax","info_message":"Sales tax in the U.S."}}},"vat_label":"Add Intra-Community VAT","vat_label_extra_info":"(Only for purchases as a company or self-employed individual)","vat_label_close":"Delete Intra-Community VAT","vat_information":"If purchasing as a company or self-employed with Intra-Community VAT, your purchase is free of VAT. Make sure you have typed the correct numbers and letters from your registration.","vat_n