the payment site","argentina_tax_info":"(+ applicable taxes. <a href=\'https://atendimento.hotmart.com.br/hc/articles/360051614631--Qu%C3%A9-impuestos-pueden-tener-incidencia-fiscal-en-mi-compra-\' target=\'_blank\'>Click here</a> for more information)","tax_exempted_info":"Prices include taxes (when applicable)","shopper_location_message":"Your location and sales taxes have been updated","apply_coupon":"I have a coupon","add_coupon":"Enter the coupon","use_elo_card":"To take advantage of the discount, use your Elo card, and insert the coupon ELO50 again.","inform_elo_discount":"Use the coupon ELO50 and get a 50% discount!","card_list":{"brazil":"MasterCard, Visa, Amex, Hipercard, Hiper and Elo","global":"MasterCard, Visa and Amex"},"unitedstates":{"document":{"placeholder":"Enter your driver\'s license or passport number","placeholder_simple":"Driver\'s license or passport number","label":"ID number"}}},"checkout_wizard":{"name_label":"Hello, to purchase this product, please enter your full name:","name_placeholder":"Full name","email_label":"Now, enter the email you will use to access the product after the purchase:","email_placeholder":"Email","document_label":"For your safety, please inform your ID or Corporate number:","document_placeholder":"ID/Corporate no.","phone_label":"For your safety, please enter your phone number.","address_label":"Almost there!","state_abbrev_placeholder":"State","payment_form_label":"How do you wish to pay?","installmentNumber_label":"Do you want to split your order into how many installments?","two_cards_intro":"Which credit cards are you going to use for this purchase? ","fill_card":"Card Information"},"msg_checkout_doubt_seller":"Any doubts or questions related to the product\'s content must be sent to the the vendor.","msg_checkout_order_term_0":"In case of any problems or doubts about the purchase, such as payment options, access to the product, refund and support, please contact our team: {0}","msg_checkout_order_term_1":"This purchase will be shown in your credit card statement as made in the store","msg_checkout_order_term_2":"There is a warranty period of","msg_checkout_order_term_3":"days to request cancellation in case of defect/inconsistency with the product.","msg_checkout_order_term_4":"The delivery period for the digital product can vary depending on the payment method. For example, boleto up to 72 hours; Credit Card, up to 24 hours; Online Transfer, up to 8 hours.","msg_checkout_order_term_5":"Hotmart is a digital products distribution platform and holds no employment relationship or of any other nature other than the service delivery of technology and digital distribution to the vendors. ","msg_checkout_order_term_6":"Any additional information about the product must be provided directly by the seller after the purchase. The buyer will receive an email address to contact the seller. ","msg_checkout_order_term_7":"In case of a refund, the buyer may be refunded by bank transfer or credit card chargeback, depending on the payment method used. The refund may take up to thirty days to take place. ","msg_checkout_order_term_8":"Your contact information may be shared with the seller and/or their promotion partners.","msg_checkout_order_term_9":"This purchase and/or related affiliate commissions may be canceled if the purchase is found to have been carried out by an Affiliate using his own affiliate link.","msg_checkout_order_term_10":"This purchase and/or related affiliate commissions may be canceled if the information in the Buyer\'s details are not accurate.","msg_checkout_order_term_11":"If the purchase is being made by a buyer that has made more than one refund request, the purchase may not be approved.","msg_checkout_order_term_12":"The completion of the purchase is an acknowledgement and agreement by the buyer to the Terms of Purchase.","msg_checkout_order_term_13":"In case of any problems or doubts about the purchase, such as payment options, access to the product, refund and support, please contact our team:","msg_checkout_order_term_14":"This product was created by","msg_checkout_order_term_15":"For matters relative to the contents of this product, please contact the Producer on the email:","msg_checkout_order_term_16":"In case of refund, the credit will be reimbursed in a period of 30 to 60 days after the cancellation of the transaction.","msg_checkout_order_term_17":"Your contact information will be sent to the product\'s Author. ","msg_checkout_order_term_18":"Refund requests lead to a complete reimbursement of the purchase, never partial. This goes for all the products available at Hotmart. ","msg_checkout_order_term_19":"Terms of Use - complete version","msg_checkout_order_term_20":"The purchase of the product {0} will be made through smart installments, according to the offer and politics created under the responsibility of the Digital Producer {1}. Therefore, the buyer understands that not paying the installments will result in blocking the access to the product purchased. Besides, the Buyer with overdue payments can be stopped from making new purchases of digital products registered at the Hotmart Platform. ","msg_checkout_order_term_000":"In case of any problems or doubts about the purchase, such as payment options, access to the product, refund, and support, please","msg_checkout_order_term_001":"This product was created by","msg_checkout_order_term_002":"For matters relative to the contents of this product, please contact the producer on the email:","msg_checkout_order_term_003":"This purchase will be shown in your credit card statement as made in the store","msg_checkout_order_term_004":"However, it\'s important to highlight that this is only how the purchase will be shown in the card statement or invoice because the digital product purchased was not created by HOTMART, which bears no responsibility for its content, functionality, characteristics, offer, and advertising;","msg_checkout_order_term_005":"If the purchase of the Digital Product was made through Smart Installments, according to the offer and policies created under the responsibility of the Digital Producer, you\'re hereby aware that the not payment of any installment will result in blocking the access to the product purchased. Besides, the defaulting Buyer may be stopped from making new purchases of digital products registered at the Hotmart Platform. ","msg_checkout_order_term_006":"If this Digital Product is being offered in Free Trial Period, which represents a free usage period. The free usage period (Free Trial Period) will start when indicated by the Digital Producer and aims to allow people interested in the product to have a taste of the digital content in the abovementioned period.","msg_checkout_order_term_007":"It is important to highlight that if you do not expressly cancel the Free Trial Period at the end od the free usage period, the Digital Producer responsible for the product will automatically start charging the payment concerning the subscription of the Digital Product, whose purchase will be ruled by this Terms of Purchase. ","msg_checkout_order_term_008":"The producer of the product (Digital Producer/Seller) is solely and exclusively responsible for the digital product, in all legal and financial aspects. Any administrative or legal questions that come from the content of the purchased product, its characteristics, functionalities, offer, and advertisement should be done directly to the Producer through the email stated above or any other form of contact made available by the seller;","msg_checkout_order_term_009":"By completing the purchase, you agree and accept in whole and without restrictions the Terms of Use and Privacy Policies of the Hotmart Platform, whose complete version can be accessed through the following link <a href=\\"https://www.hotmart.com/en/tos\\" target=\\"_blank\\">link</a>. Therefore, an attentive reading of the aforementioned documents is recommended;","msg_checkout_order_term_010":"There is a warranty period of","msg_checkout_order_term_011":"days, ensured by the Producer, to request the cancellation of the purchase in the case of any defect/inconsitency of the product;","msg_checkout_order_term_012":"The cancellation deadline mentioned above will start from the moment the purchase is completed. Therefore, you, the buyer, are responsible for immediately verifying if the access to the digital product works properly. Accordingly, if there are technical problems, duly proved by the buyer, to access the content purchased, the deadline for the cancellation will be suspended until the problem is solved, when it will resume counting from when it started. ","msg_checkout_order_term_013":"The deadline for the delivery of the digital product can vary according to the payment method used, for example: Credit Card up to 24h, Wire Transfer up to 8h. ","msg_checkout_order_term_014":"Hotmart is a digital products distribution platform and holds no employment relationship or of any other nature other than the service delivery of technology and digital distribution to the vendors. Therefore, it is important to emphasize that Hotmart is not legally and/or financially liable for the digital product purchased, once its content, functionality, quality, offer and, advertisement, are of sole responsibility of the Digital Producer who created it and made it available on the platform;","msg_checkout_order_term_015":"Any additional information about the product must be obtained by the buyer straight from the seller (Digital Producer) after the purchase. The buyer will receive an email address where to contact the seller.","msg_checkout_order_term_016":"In the case of a refund, the buyer will be refunded via wire transfer or credit card chargeback, depending on the payment method used at the time of the purchase. The refund can take up to thirty days to be completed in the case of a wire transfer and, from 30 to 60 days when via credit card chargeback.","msg_checkout_order_term_017":"Your contact information, such as email, phone number, etc., may be sent to the seller e/or the seller\'s promotion partner. ","msg_checkout_order_term_018":"This purchase and/or related affiliate commissions may be canceled if the purchase is found to have been carried out by an Affiliate using his own affiliate link.","msg_checkout_order_term_019":"This purchase may be revoked and/or the affiliate commissions canceled if the Buyer\'s information is not completely filled in with truthful information about the Buyer.  ","msg_checkout_order_term_020":"If the purchase is being made by a buyer that has made more than one refund request, the purchase may not be approved.","msg_checkout_order_term_021":"Completing a purchase confirms the buyer\'s understanding and agreement with our Terms of Purchase.","msg_checkout_order_term_022":"Refund requests involve the return of the total amount of the purchase and are never partial. This applies to all products made available at the Hotmart Platform by Digital Producers. ","msg_checkout_order_term_023":"The purchase of the DIGITAL PRODUCT has been made by means of Smart Installments, in accordance with the offer and policies created under the responsibilities of the PRODUCER. Therefore, the BUYER is aware that by not paying any portion of the payments will result in their access to the DIGITAL PRODUCT being blocked. In addition to this, the BUYER may be prevented from making future purchases of DIGITAL PRODUCTS registered on the Hotmart platform. ","msg_oney_term":"With 3x 4x Oney, you can pay for your purchase in 3, 4, 6, 10 or 12 installments with your bank card, from a value of € 90 and up to € 2,500 (a minimum installment of € 20, the values ​​and conditions available may vary depending on the circumstances). All charges will be made periodically to your card. Please note that the first payment will be made at the time of purchase. Valid for VISA or Mastercard, debit or credit cards, with an expiration date greater than the duration of the selected financing modality. For example, if you apply for financing for six months, your card\'s expiration date cannot be less than six months. We do not accept prepaid, virtual, or American Express cards. Only applicable to individuals, of legal age, living in Spain. 3x 4x Oney is a payment method that allows purchase in installments offered by Oney Servicios Financieros EFC, a financial institution registered and supervised by the Bank of Spain under number 8814. You can find more information about 3x 4x Oney <a href = \' https://www.oney.es/aviso-legal/informacion-legal-3x4xoney \'target =\' _ blank \'> here </a>. For any questions related to deferred payment, contact Oney at the following email cliente3x4x@Oney.es","msg_checkout_closed_order":"We appreciate your interest, but sales of this product are temporarily closed. ","msg_checkout_ccv":"CVV or security code are the three <br />digits on the back of your card. ","msg_checkout_subscription_monthly":"*Subscription value is charged in your card monthly. ","msg_checkout_subscription_bimonthly":"*Subscription value is charged in your card bimonthly. ","msg_checkout_subscription_quarterly":"*Subscription value is charged in your card quarterly. ","msg_checkout_subscription_biannual":"*Subscription value is charged in your card every six months. ","msg_checkout_subscription_annual":"*Subscription value is charged in your card annually. ","label_checkout_cc_name_mobile":"Name written <br />on card","label_checkout_cc_expire_date_mobile":"<br />Expiration date","msg_checkout_billet_0":"Boleto (one-time payment)","msg_checkout_billet_1":"Please pay attention to the details:","msg_checkout_billet_2":"Payments by boleto take <b>up to 3 calendar days</b> to be cleared and then the products are sent.","msg_checkout_billet_3":"Pay attention to the due date on the Boleto. You can pay at any bank or lottery shop before the due date (Brazil).","msg_checkout_billet_4":"After the payment has been made, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)","msg_checkout_billet_5":"You will get a Boleto for each subscription payment.","msg_checkout_billet_6":"Discount is valid until {0}ª charge ","msg_checkout_multibanco_0":"After payment confirmation, you\'ll have access to the product.","msg_checkout_multibanco_1":"Please pay attention to the details:","msg_checkout_multibanco_2":"Pay attention to the due date on the invoice. It can be paid in any ATM (in Portugal) or Homebanking ","msg_checkout_multibanco_3":"After the payment has been made, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)","msg_checkout_multibanco_4":"Multibanco is only available for <b>payments in full.</b>","msg_checkout_paypal_0":"Use PayPal for one-time payments and subscriptions","msg_checkout_paypal_1":"Click on the button below to be redirected to PayPal and pay attention to the details:","msg_checkout_paypal_2":"PayPal takes payment with MasterCard, Visa and Amex credit cards.","msg_checkout_paypal_3":"After the payment has been made, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)","msg_checkout_paypal_4":"PayPal only accepts payment with {0}.","msg_checkout_samsungpay_0":"Click on the button below to be redirected to SamsungPay and pay attention to the details:","msg_checkout_samsungpay_1":"SamsungPay accepts payment with MasterCard and Visa credit cards.","msg_checkout_samsungpay_2":"After the payment has been made, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)","msg_checkout_googlepay_0":"Google Pay (one-time payment only)","msg_checkout_googlepay_1":"Click on the button below to be redirected to Google Pay and pay attention to the details:","msg_checkout_googlepay_2":"Google Pay accepts payment with  MasterCard, Visa, Amex, Hipercard, Hiper and Elo.","msg_checkout_googlepay_3":"After the payment has been made, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)","msg_checkout_googlepay_4":"Google Pay accepts payment with {0}.","msg_checkout_hotmart_0":"Pay with Hotmart Account","msg_checkout_hotmart_1":"The Hotmart account accepts payments with credit cards or remaining account balance. ","msg_checkout_hotmart_2":"If you pay for the product with your account balance, it will be directly deducted  from your Hotmart Account","msg_checkout_hotmart_3":"Payment in installments is only permitted for credit card payments","msg_checkout_hotmart_1_int":"With your Hotmart account, you can use the credit card you have saved on the platform.  ","msg_checkout_hotmart_2_int":"The Hotmart account accepts payments with credit cards in lump sums or installments   ","msg_checkout_hotmartpay_3":"After the payment has been made, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)","msg_checkout_hotmartpay_4":"Login with your Hotmart account:","msg_checkout_hotmartpay_5":"Your current balance is:","msg_checkout_hotmartpay_6":"Pay with","msg_checkout_hotmartpay_7":"Hotmart Balance","msg_checkout_hotmartpay_8":"+ Card","msg_checkout_safetypay_banks":"Available banks:","msg_checkout_safetypay_method":"Payment via:","msg_checkout_safetypay_1":"See the available Banks:","msg_checkout_safetypay_2":"When selecting this option, you will be redirected to a secure bank transfer payment page.","msg_checkout_safetypay_3":"In this page, you must complete your payment in up to 20 minutes.","msg_checkout_safetypay_4":"You will also receive payment instructions, and should enter the information requested. ","msg_checkout_safetypay_5":"IMPORTANT! This purchase will feature on your Credit Card Statement as:","msg_checkout_safetypay_bb":"Banco do Brasil","msg_checkout_safetypay_itau":"Itaú","msg_checkout_safetypay_bradesco":"Bradesco","msg_checkout_safetypay_caixa":"Caixa Econômica Federal","msg_checkout_safetypay_santander":"Santander","msg_checkout_safetypay_banrisul":"Banrisul","msg_checkout_spei_1":"How to pay with","msg_checkout_spei_2":"<li>SPEI allows you to make <b>one-time payments</b> and wire transfers with your Internet Banking.</li><li>After clicking the <b>Generate payment slip button</b>, a slip will be generated with the data necessary to make the payment.</li><li>With the slip generated, access your bank\'s Internet Banking system and make a transfer using the payment data you\'ve received.</li><li>After payment, check your email to receive access data for the product proof of payment (also check the SPAM box).</li><li>Payments using SPEI are confirmed in realtime.</li><b>Important:</b> The payment slip for SPEI is valid for 3 days. After this period, it will not be possible to make the payment and you will have to generate another slip.</li>","msg_checkout_installment_tax":"*Installments with a {0} monthly fee","msg_checkout_installment_tax_generic":"*The installment amount has an additional fee.","msg_checkout_installment_no_tax":"*There is no installment fee","msg_checkout_paypal_processing_1":"Hotmart is processing this order at the request of","msg_checkout_paypal_processing_2":", by proceeding you agree with the","msg_checkout_order_doubled_request":"There is an order request in progress. To avoid duplicity, please start the purchase process again. ","msg_checkout_exchange_rate_error":"We apologize, but it was not possible to make a currency translation for this product.","msg_checkout_unauthorized_purchase":"Purchase not authorized","msg_checkout_purchase_already_performed":"You have already made the purchase of this product","msg_recurrency_first_card":"Attention: The recurrences will be charged to this card.  ","msg_widget_checkout_invalid_cupom":"Invalid Code :-(","msg_checkout_card_expiration":"The card expiration date is not compatible with the number of installments chosen. Please, choose to pay in fewer installments or change cards. ","msg_checkout_iban":"*The IBAN number is your country code followed by your bank account number. For example, GB90 + bank account number. If you still don\'t know what your IBAN number is, please ask your bank manager.","msg_checkout_caixa_virtual_debit_1":"Caixa Virtual debit card (Brazil)","msg_checkout_caixa_virtual_debit_2":"Use the Virtual Card generated by the Caixa app (Brazil) or on Caixa Internet Banking","msg_checkout_caixa_virtual_debit_3":"If you have already used your card today, remember that the daily limit is BRL 2,000.00.","label_checkout_close":"Close","label_checkout_cupon":"<br /> Discount Coupon","label_checkout_cupon2":"Do you have a discount coupon?","title_checkout_order_term":"Terms of Purchase","label_checkout_seller":"The product\'s seller is","label_checkout_select_country":"Select your country","label_checkout_section_1":"Registration data","label_checkout_full_name":"Full name","label_checkout_email":"Email","label_checkout_cpf":"Taxpayer Identification Number","label_checkout_why":"Why?","label_checkout_phone":"Mobile","label_checkout_ref":"REF.","label_checkout_section_2":"Your address","label_checkout_state":"State","label_checkout_city":"City","label_checkout_district":"District","label_checkout_address":"Address","label_checkout_address_number":"Number","label_checkout_address_complement":"Complement","label_checkout_other":"Other","label_checkout_zip_code":"Post Code","label_checkout_zip_code_international":"ZIP Code","label_checkout_section_3":"Payment method","label_checkout_cc":"Credit Cards","label_checkout_billet":"Boleto","label_checkout_paypal":"PayPal","label_checkout_balance":"Balance","label_checkout_cc_number":"Card number","label_checkout_cc_name":"Name written on card","label_checkout_cc_name_short":"Name on card","label_checkout_cc_expire_date":"Expiration date","label_checkout_cc_expire_date_component":"Expiration","label_checkout_ccv":"Enter the CVV /<br />Security code","label_checkout_cvv":"Enter the security code","label_checkout_installment":"Installment","label_checkout_discount_coupon":"Do you have a discount coupon?","label_checkout_monthly":"{0} / month","label_checkout_bimonthly":"{0} / two months","label_checkout_quarterly":"{0} / quarter","label_checkout_biannual":"{0} / semester ","label_checkout_annual":"{0} / year","label_installments_options_checkout_monthly":"{0} times of {1} */ month","label_installments_options_checkout_bimonthly":"{0} times of {1} */ two months","label_installments_options_checkout_quarterly":"{0} times of {1} */ quarter","label_installments_options_checkout_biannual":"{0} times of {1} */ semester","label_installments_options_checkout_annual":"{0} times of {1} */ year","label_checkout_special_recurring_message":"From {1} no. {0} on, {2} will be charged","label_checkout_trial_title":"Free Trial","label_checkout_trial_period_days":"You will have {0} day(s) to try the product for free.","label_checkout_trial_period_tasting":"You will have {0} day(s) to try the product.","label_checkout_trial_cancel_message":"During this period you are able to cancel the subscription at any time without any fee.","label_checkout_trial_recorrency":"After this period you will be charged ","label_checkout_trial_message":"A symbolical value will be processed on your card just to validate it. This amount will not be charged to your invoice.","label_checkout_trial_thanks_message":"Your purchase was completed on trial mode. Purchase expires on the {0} and from then on {1} will be charged.","label_checkout_unique_charge":"{0}","label_installments_options_checkout_unique_charge":"{0} times of {1} ","label_checkout_x":"times of","label_checkout_discount":"Discount","label_checkout_total":"Total","label_checkout_and_card":"+ Card","label_checkout_invoice":"Joining fee + monthly fee","label_checkout_insufficient_balance":"Insufficient balance","label_checkout_pick_another_payment_method":"Please choose a different payment method","label_checkout_login_with_you_hotmart_account":"Login with your Hotmart account:","label_checkout_hotmart_account":"Hotmart Account","label_checkout_current_balance":"Your current balance is:","label_checkout_show_all_saved_cards":"Show all my saved cards","label_checkout_add_new_card":"New credit card","button_checkout_search":"Search","button_checkout_back":"Back","button_checkout_paypal":"Pay with PayPal","button_checkout_samsungpay":"Pay with","button_checkout_balance":"Pay with balance","button_checkout_subscription":"Subscribe now","button_checkout_order_now":"Buy now","button_checkout_finish_order":"Complete Order","button_checkout_generate_billet":"Issue Boleto","button_checkout_validate_cupon":"Validate Coupon","button_checkout_ok":"Update country","button_checkout_login":"Login Hotmart","button_checkout_new_card":"Register new card","button_checkout_pay_with":"Pay with","button_checkout_login_sparkle":"Login Sparkle","button_checkout_login_only":"Login","button_checkout_sparkle":"Sparkle","button_checkout_scan_qrcode":"Or scan the QR Code with Sparkle:","button_checkout_spei":"Generate payment slip","button_checkout_use_sparkle":"Or login with your Sparkle account:","button_checkout_generate_transaction":"Generate Transaction","data_tip_checkout_country":"Click to change country","data_tip_checkout_cpf":"This is a matter of safety. The payment service will analyze if the National ID Number/ Corporate Tax Number is in accordance with the information provided by the user, such as address, card information, etc. By checking this information, we will be able to verify if the purchase is legitimate, avoiding possible frauds. ","data_tip_checkout_zip":"I don\'t know my ZIP code, what do I do? It\'s easy. If you\'re in Brazil, just access www.buscacep.correios.com.br. If you\'re in the US, access https://tools.usps.com/go/ZipLookupAction_input. Informing your address, even for a digital product, is a matter of safety. There is a team that analyzes all the transactions to ensure that the purchase is being made by you, cross analyzing buyer\'s information. ","data_tip_checkout_accept_cc":"We take VISA, MASTER, AMEX and HIPERCARD. Just choose your card below. ","data_tip_checkout_accept_billet":"We accept payment via Boleto.","data_tip_checkout_accept_paypal":"We accept payment via PayPal.","data_tip_checkout_accept_hotmart":"Pay with your balance at Hotmart.","checkout":{"terms_of_service_agreement":{"label":"I\'m aware that Hotmart is processing {AUTHOR_NAME}\'s service request and I agree with the {PURCHASE_TERMS} and confirm that I have read and understood the {PRIVACY_POLICY}.","purchase_terms":"Terms of Purchase","privacy_policy":"Privacy Policy","privacy_policy_url":"https://www.hotmart.com/legal/en/data-privacy-policy"},"create_default":{"browser_not_supported":"Unfortunately we do not support your browser (Internet Explorer) :(","please_use_the_supported_browsers":"Please use <a href=\\"http://www.google.com/chrome/\\" target=\\"_blank\\" title=\\"Google Chrome\\">Google Chrome</a> or <a href=\\"http://www.mozilla.org/firefox\\" target=\\"_blank\\" title=\\"Firefox\\">Firefox</a>","to_create_the_best_theme_possible":"To create the best theme possible!"},"why_inform_my_cpf_cnpj":"Why do I have to inform my National ID Number/Corporate Tax Number?","eticket":{"session":"Your reservation expires in","lote":"Lot","informations":"Information about your ticket","time":"Reservation period","untransferible":"non-transferable ticket"},"shopper_data_consent":"I accept to receive product communications via email"},"order":{"checkout":{"recovery":{"invalid_billet":"The period to validate your purchase has expired. Please make the purchase again."},"orderprocessor":{"region_not_available":"It\'s not possible to make a subscription sale for your region. ","help":"Need any help?","balance_hotmart_debit":"Debit relate to the purchase of product {0} with transaction {0}.","hotpay_error_000":"National transaction successfully approved ","hotpay_error_001":"Your purchase has been declined by credit card issuer. Please try again with a different card or choose a different payment method. For more details, contact your credit card provider.","hotpay_error_002":"It looks like there might be some restrictions on this card. Please, double-check the information you entered, try again with another card or choose another form of payment. For more details, get in touch with the card provider.  ","hotpay_error_003":"The card-issuing bank is unavailable. Please try again with a different payment method or wait a few minutes to rerun the transaction. ","hotpay_error_004":"Your security code is invalid. Please re-enter the code and try again or choose a different payment method.","hotpay_error_005":"International transaction successfully approved. ","hotpay_error_006":"Your credit card information is invalid. Please re-enter the information and try again or choose a different payment method.","hotpay_error_007":"Your credit card number is invalid. Please re-enter the number and try again or choose a different payment method.","hotpay_error_008":"Your credit card funds is insufficient. Please try again with a different card or choose a different payment method.","hotpay_error_009":"Card is expired. Try again with a different card or choose a different payment method.","hotpay_error_010":"The card was not unlocked by the card holder. Please try again with a different card or choose a different payment method. For more details, please contact your credit card provider. ","hotpay_error_011":"The card information is invalid. Please re-enter the information and try again or choose a different payment method.","hotpay_error_012":"Debit card is not supported. Please use a credit card.","hotpay_error_013":"Nonexistent transaction. There is no transaction for the identifier informed.","hotpay_error_014":"It looks like there might be some restrictions on this card. Please, double-check the information you entered, try again with another card or choose another form of payment. ","hotpay_error_015":"Invalid number of installments. The number of installments is higher than the number allowed. ","hotpay_error_016":"The card used only allows DEBIT purchases. Please try again with a different card or choose a different payment method.","hotpay_error_017":"The card security code was not provided. Please provide the security code and try again.","hotpay_error_018":"Incorrect use of security code identifier. Please enter the security code and try to make the purchase again. ","hotpay_error_019":"Card number not informed. Please enter card number and try to make the purchase again. ","hotpay_error_020":"The card expiration date was not provided. Please provide the expiration date and try again.","hotpay_error_021":"Ooh! This transaction was refused due to some sort of restriction. Please, double-check the info on the card, use a different card or choose another form of payment.  ","hotpay_error_022":"Unknown error. Please try again. ","hotpay_error_023":"Oh no! The transaction was refused! Please, double-check the information on the card, use a different card or choose another form of payment. ","hotpay_error_024":"There is some sort of restriction with the information entered. Please verify the information and try to make the purchase again.","hotpay_error_025":"This session has been used before. Please try again. If the mistakes persists, please select another payment method. ","hotpay_error_026":"The card expiration date is invalid. Please re-enter the expiration date and try again.","hotpay_error_027":"The card used does not allow to buy in installments. Please try again with a different card or choose a different payment method.","hotpay_error_028":"Pending transaction.","hotpay_error_029":"You need to provide a document in order to start a subscription paying with Boleto.","hotpay_error_030":"The transaction could not be processed. Please contact the card operator.","hotpay_error_031":"The document informed is invalid","hotpay_error_032":"We\'ve already identified an order approved for this email in the past few hours. Please, check your inbox.","hotpay_error_033":"Error connecting to SamsungPay","hotpay_error_034":"The card expiration date is not compatible with the number of installments chosen. Please, choose to pay in fewer installments or change cards. ","hotpay_error_036":"Insufficient balance. ","hotpay_error_037":"Check if you\'ve typed in your information correctly and try again. Or, use another form of payment. ","hotpay_error_038":"Invalid PIN","hotpay_error_039":"The coupon for this sale has expired. Please remove it to make the purchase.","hotpay_error_040":"Debit cards can\'t be used to make installment payments, but you can try again with a credit card.","hotpay_error_041":"The order could not be completed. Transaction rejected due to some sort of restriction.","hotpay_error_042":"Transaction cannot be completed. The buyer should contact PayPal to see if there are any restrictions on the account.","hotpay_error_043":"Your purchase could not be completed because your credit assessment has not been approved. You can try again in the future.","hotpay_error_045":"To transfer or use your balance, you need to register a bank account with Hotmart and wait for it to be verified, which can take up to 5 days.","hotpay_error_047":"There\'s an issue with this card. Check if it is enabled for online purchases, or contact your bank.","adyen_error_903":"Internal error. Please try again.","hotmart_checkout_error_hmc_000":"Invalid payment request.","hotmart_checkout_error_hmc_001":"Affiliation not found.","hotmart_checkout_error_hmc_002":"Affiliation is not active.","hotmart_checkout_error_hmc_003":"Maximum limit of affiliation reached.","hotmart_checkout_error_hmc_004":"This product is not yet available for sale.","hotmart_checkout_error_hmc_005":"Product unavailable.","hotmart_checkout_error_hmc_006":"Products with different currencies.","hotmart_checkout_error_hmc_007":"Producer\'s address not found.","hotmart_checkout_error_hmc_008":"Offer not found.","hotmart_checkout_error