re than 72 hours since you made the payment and you still haven\'t received your access information, please contact the vendor so that they may look into this situation. ","check_your_email_and_spam":"ATTENTION: Check your email (and your SPAM folder)","check_your_email_and_spam_2":"ATTENTION: Check your email ({0}) and your SPAM folder.","check_your_email_warning":"If the email is not correct, please contact our support team. ","contact_the_author_after_three_days":"If it\'s been more than 72 hours since you made the payment and you still haven\'t received your access information, please contact the author so that they may look into this situation. ","complete_registration_and_you_will_receive_access_after_payment_confirmation":"Your order has been registered. Now, complete your registration and make the payment. After the Boleto has been paid and confirmed, you will receive an email message with the access information. ","order_received_being_analyzed":"We\'ve received your request and it is already being processed by the system.","order_subscription_trial":"you can now try out the product for {0} day(s). At the end of this period, you will get an email at","as_soon_as_billet_generated":"As soon as your Boleto is issued, you\'ll receive an email at","as_soon_as_multibanco_generated":"As soon as your bank payment slip is generated, you\'ll receive an email at","trial_authorised":"Congratulations! Now, you can try out this product for {0} day(s).","with_instructions_to_payment":"with the payment instructions."},"credit_card_order_complete":{"order_received":"Order successfully received!","payment_being_analyzed_check_your_email":"Your payment is \\"Under analysis\\". Check your email to keep track of your purchase. ","order_received_being_analyzed":"We have received your order and it is been processed by the system. ","when_can_i_access_the_product":"When will I have access to the product/service?","as_soon_as_credit_card_aproves":"As soon as the credit card operator and the payment service have approved the purchase, you will receive an email message at","with_instructions_to_access_product":"with the instructions to access the product. ","why_is_my_payment_under_analysis":"Why is my payment \\"Under Analysis\\"?","check_your_spam_box":"<b>IMPORTANT:</b> Remember to also check your SPAM folder, because, depending on your email service, our message may end up in there by mistake. ","credit_card_analysis_explanation":"For purchases with credit card, our payment services requires a verification period that may vary from a few minutes to 48 hours, in which the authenticity of the information provided at the moment of purchase is verified, thus ensuring safety for our buyers. This procedure prevents fraud and allows us to offer a safer environment for you to make your purchases. ","this_purchase_will_show_on_bill_as":"<b>Important:</b> this purchase will appear on your <b>statement</b> as:"},"samsung_pay_order_complete":{"wait_transaction_completed":"Just a moment, your order is being completed.","payment_refused_verify_credit_card":"The payment has been refused. But not all is lost. Check for possible errors shown on this page or contact your credit card issuer.","payment_refused":"Your payment has been refused."},"picpay_order_complete":{"order_made":"Request made!","success":"Now, you just need to finish the payment.","purchase_reserved":"your purchase has been reserved and is waiting for payment.","download_step_1":"Download the PicPay app on your phone: at the AppStore for iPhone, or PlayStore for Android. ","download_step_2":"Open PicPay and follow the instructions above.","download_step_2_mobile":"Open PicPay and scan the code that appears when you click on Pay with PicPay.","download_step_3":"After the payment, you will get an email with your product\'s access information (check your SPAM box if needed). ","pay_the":"Pay the","pay_step_1":"Open PicPay on your phone","pay_step_2":"Tap the code icon in the upper bar","pay_step_3":"Point your camera at the code and continue with your payment","watch_your_mail":"Couldn\'t find your access email? In some cases, your email provider might have put our email in your SPAM folder. Check your SPAM box because your payment details might be there. ","contact_the_vendor":"If after 72 hours you still haven\'t gotten your access information, contact the seller so they can check the situation.","no_account":"Don\'t have a PicPay account?","download_free":"Download the app for free","pay_with":"Pay with","payment_details_title":"Details on payment with PicPay:"},"pix_order_complete":{"order_made":"Order made!","order_pending":"Now, you just need to finish the payment","congratulations":"Congratulations,","success":"Your order has been approved!","pending":" Your order is being processed.","pay_info_1_title":"Immediate","pay_info_1":"Make your payment in just a few seconds, no additional costs","pay_info_2_title":"Simple","pay_info_2":"To pay, just open your bank\'s app, search for PIX and scan the QRcode","pay_info_3_title":"Safe","pay_info_3":"PIX payment was developed by the Central Bank of Brazil to make your payments simpler","pay_info_4":"<strong>Payments using PIX are currently unavailable for the following banks:</strong> BRB, Cora, DayCoval, Neon, PJBank, Sicoob, Sofisa, SuperDigital. If you have any questions, please contact your bank.","pay_info_subscription_title":"Recurring","pay_info_subscription":"You will receive a PIX code by email for each recurring payment of the subscription.","payment_details_title":"Pay with","pay_steps_copy":"PIX copy and paste: open your bank\'s app n your cell phone, select PIX, and make the payment. Or scan the code with a cell phone.","pay_steps_scan":"Hi, {0}! We\'ve saved your order and it\'s awaiting payment","pay_steps_scan_subscription":"Hi, {0}! Your subscription registration is complete. Make the payment to access your product","pay_steps_scan_1":"Hello,","pay_steps_scan_2":"Your purchase is awaiting p