ct Debit Adyen will notify you 3 working days in advance of your account being debited or as otherwise agreed. If you request Adyen to collect a payment, confirmation of the amount and date will be given to you at the time of the request.","debit_guarantee_description_2":"If an error is made in the payment of your Direct Debit, by Adyen or your bank or building society, you are entitled to a full and immediate refund of the amount paid from your bank or building society.","debit_guarantee_description_3":"You can cancel a Direct Debit at any time by simply contacting your bank or building society. Written confirmation may be required. Please also notify us."}},"login":{"email_user_placeholder":"Enter your email or username ","email_placeholder":"Enter your email","password_placeholder":"Enter your password","login_continue":"Log in to continue:","back":"Back","show_password":"Show password","enter":"Login","forgot_password":"Forgot your password?","recover_password":"Recover my password","login_sparkle":"Log in with Sparkle","password_email_instructions":"Fill in the field below with your email address to receive instructions on how to create a new Hotmart password","password_email_instructions_success":"Instructions on how to create a new password for your Hotmart account have been sent to your email.","logged_with":"You are logged in with:","alter_account":"Change account","choose_payment_methods":"Select payment method(s):","balance_available":"Available balance:","no_balance":"No available balance","card_installment_warning":"Only payments made with credit cards can be paid in installments. ","login_by":"Login via","recaptcha_terms":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA, and the Google {PrivacyPolicy} and  {TermsOfService} apply.  ","terms_of_service":"Terms of Use","privacy_policy":"Privacy Policy","sparkle_step1":"Open Hotmart Sparkle on your smartphone","sparkle_step2a":"Click the button","sparkle_step2b":"in the upper-right corner ","sparkle_step3":"Aim your camera at the following code:","collaborator_login_message":"You\'re accessing this feature using <b>{0}</b>, but you don\'t have permission to use this account. Log in with your account to make payments with your Hotmart Account. ","errors":{"SECURITY_0001":"Inactive user","SECURITY_0002":"Maximum login attempts exceeded. You need to reset your password.","SECURITY_0003":"Username or password invalid.","SECURITY_0004":"Access denied","SECURITY_0005":"Your account cannot be closed due to a pending receivable balance.","SECURITY_0006":"Your password has been recently reset","SECURITY_0007":"Fields \'New Password\' and \'Confirm New Password\' don\'t match","SECURITY_0008":"Current password incorrect.","SECURITY_0009":"Invalid or expired Token","SECURITY_0010":"There already is a user with this email address","SECURITY_0011":"User is not in service","SECURITY_0012":"Assistance is not accepted","SECURITY_0013":"Security code not generated","SECURITY_0014":"Security code already used","SECURITY_0015":"Security code expired","SECURITY_0016":"Invalid security code","SECURITY_0017":"User account suspended","SECURITY_0024":"The password must contain at least 7 characters with letters and numbers."}},"paypal_payments":{"credit":{"instructions_title":"PayPal Credit:","instructions":{"0":"Buy now, pay later with PayPal Credit","1":"If approved, PayPal Credit is automatically added to your PayPal account. Check out in just a few clicks with no card numbers or expiration dates","2":"After the payment has been made, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)"}},"venmo":{"instructions_title":"Venmo","instructions":{"0":"You can use your Venmo account to make a payment. Simply tap the PayPal/Venmo button and a Venmo payment option will appear on the next screen","1":"Make sure you have the Venmo app installed on your mobile phone and have already opted-in to make payments online","2":"After the payment has been made, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)"}}},"cash_payments":{"baloto":{"name":"Baloto","instructions_title":"How does the payment via Baloto works:","button_generate_text":"Issue Baloto","instructions":{"0":"Baloto is only available for <b>payments in full.</b>","1":"On the next screen, a voucher will be generated for this purchase.","2":"You can make the payment in a Baloto store of your preference. Keep in mind the voucher expires after 3 calendar days.","3":"The payment will be confirmed in up to 72 hours.","4":"After the payment is confirmed, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)."}},"oxxo":{"name":"Oxxo","instructions_title":"How does the payment via OXXO works:","button_generate_text":"Issue Oxxo","instructions":{"0":"OXXO is only available for <b>payments in full.</b>","1":"On the next screen, a OXXO voucher will be generated for this purchase.","2":"Go to an OXXO store and inform the boleta number at the cashier.","3":"The payment will be confirmed in up to three business days.","4":"After the payment is confirmed, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)."}},"cupon_pago":{"name":"Cupón de Pago","instructions_title":"How does the payment via Cupón de Pago works:","button_generate_text":"Issue Cupón de Pago","instructions":{"0":"Cupón de Pago is only available for <b>payments in full.</b>","1":"On the next screen, an invoice will be generated with the information related to the payment of your purchase (reference code).","2":"Depending on the establishment you choose, the barcode and/or reference code may be requested. Therefore it is recommended that you print the invoice or present it on your mobile phone.","3":"Go to any of these establishments to pay for your invoice: PagoFacil, RapiPago, CobroExpress PampaPagos, BaproPagos, PagoListo, ChubutPagos, Provincia Pagos, Formopagos, ProntoPago and Ripsa. You have up to 3 calendar days to make the payment.","4":"Payment confirmation will take 12 to 72 hours.","5":"After the payment is confirmed, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)."}},"pago_efectivo":{"name":"PagoEfectivo","instructions_title":"How does the payment via PagoEfectivo works:","button_generate_text":"Issue PagoEfectivo","instructions":{"0":"PagoEfectivo is only available for <b>payments in full.</b>","1":"On the next screen, a PagoEfectivo code will be generated for this purchase.","2":"You can pay cash in one of the brick and mortar establishments or Internet Banking. Invoice expires in: 3 calendar days","3":"When the transaction is confirmed, you\'ll get a purchase receipt. The payment is confirmed in 12 to 72 hours.","4":"As soon as the payment has been confirmed, you\'ll gett an email with the product access data (make sure to check your SPAM)."}},"sencillito":{"name":"Sencillito","instructions_title":"How does the payment via Sencillito works:","button_generate_text":"Issue Sencillito ","instructions":{"0":"Sencillito is only available for <b>payments in full.</b>","1":"On the next screen, you\'ll enter your information to generate a Sencillito invoice.","2":"Bring the invoice to one of the Sencillito affiliate stores and pay cash or with a pre-paid card. Invoice expires in: 3 calendar days","3":"When the transaction is confirmed, you\'ll be given a receipt. The payment is confirmed between 12 to 72 hours.","4":"After the payment is confirmed, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)."}},"installments":{"instructions_title":"Pay for your purchase in installments using bank payment slips.","instructions_subtitle":"Information on installment payment with bank payment slips:","credit_instruction":"Make the purchases you want without using up your available credit card limit","invoice_instruction":"Pay the bank payment slips we\'ll send to your email every month","how_many":"Choose in how many installments you want to pay","select":"Select an option:","option":"{0} monthly payments","price":"of {0}","total_value":"Total amount","total_installments":"{0} installments of {1}","warning":"Every month, <b>you will receive a new bank payment slip until you\'ve paid all installments.</b> Make sure you pay them until their due date to avoid default.","term":"I understand that <b>bank payment slips</b> will be sent to <b>{0}</b> every month and <b>they must be paid until the last installment</b>, regardless of the length of the product purchased.","instructions":{"0":"After you\'ve paid the bank payment slip, it can take up to 3 business days to confirm payment and clear your access to the product. ","1":"Check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder)","2":"Pay attention to the due date on the Bank Payment Slip. You can pay it at any bank or lottery shop until its due date."}}},"online_bank_transfer_klarna":{"header_title":"Online bank transfer","instructions_title":"How to pay with an online bank transfer:","steps":{"1":{"title":"Simple and no registration","text":"Just choose your bank, authenticate your account and make the online transfer."},"2":{"title":"100% Secure","text":"Your transfer is made in a cryptographed environment and your information is protected."},"3":{"title":"Immediate confirmation","text":"Your transfer is made right away and payment confirmation is instant.*"}},"about":{"0":"Make a secure payment with an online bank transfer <b>Pay Now / SOFORT</b> from Klarna.","1":"When selecting this option, you will be redirected to a secure bank transfer payment page.","2":"To make a transfer, you must choose one of the banks available and be authenticated in a secure way on the online system of the chosen institution. <b>Important: Your bank account needs to be authorized to carry out online transfers.</b>","3":"After the payment has been made, check your email inbox for the access information (also check your SPAM folder).","4":"* Subject to service availabili